section.div: Dockerized Host service for LA1TV studio Clocks, using PixiJS
A service used with CasparCG Server software for scanning media located on the server. Queried with query and thumbnail commands through CasparCG Server using AMCP.
A simple browser-based studio clock for radio or television studios.
BorealDirector is a facility scale broadcast orchestration and automation suite.
